      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1109 - Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) said:\n\"Indeed, the truly blind are those who are blind in their hearts, for it is not the eyes that go blind but the hearts within the chests.\""
